17
00:01:13,700 --> 00:01:14,600
I feel much better now.

18
00:01:14,880 --> 00:01:15,560
Don't worry.

19
00:01:15,800 --> 00:01:17,820
I was chatting with her
about yesterday's incident.

20
00:01:17,830 --> 00:01:19,760
