a good job looking after me.

23
00:01:25,160 --> 00:01:26,140
There's no need to worry.

24
00:01:26,720 --> 00:01:27,880
Yuhan, I'm truly honored

25
00:01:28,880 --> 00:01:29,800
by your acknowledgment.

26
00:01:30,110 --> 00:01:31,560
You two are quite close already, huh?

27
00:01:32,020 --> 00:01:32,680
Are you hungry?

28
00:01:33,040 --> 00:01:33,940
Do you want some food?

29
00:01:33,950 --> 00:01:34,860
I'll make some for you.

30
00:01:35,240 --> 00:01:36,840
Do you want steamed food or fried food?

31
00:01:37,840 --> 00:01:38,280
She can

32
00:01:39,360 --> 00:01:39,880
make both.

33
00:01:43,560 --> 00:01:44,960
