when you're in danger.

42
00:02:10,560 --> 00:02:11,600
I was reckless yesterday.

43
00:02:11,880 --> 00:02:12,760
I injured Mo Shenhai.

44
00:02:12,770 --> 00:02:14,830
I'm afraid it won't be
that easy to clean up the mess.

45
00:02:14,840 --> 00:02:15,560
What?

46
00:02:16,600 --> 00:02:17,800
You guys injured Mo Shenhai?

47
00:02:18,120 --> 00:02:19,200
You were harmed before this.

48
00:02:19,410 --> 00:02:22,040
I suspect that Mo Shenhai sent
the mysterious figure as a warning.

49
00:02:22,440 --> 00:02:23,840
I instructed Aojue to injure him.

50
00:02:25,320 --> 00:02:26,040
But Ao,

51
00:02:26,680 --> 00:02:28,320
it was better if he killed him outright.

52
00:02:28,880 --> 00:02:29,840
Now, he's half-dead.

53
00:02:30,400 --> 00:02:31,440
