81
00:03:44,920 --> 00:03:45,880
can you do me a favor?

82
00:03:46,680 --> 00:03:47,160
Go ahead.

83
00:03:49,520 --> 00:03:51,760
It's inconvenient for me
to move around due to my injury.

84
00:03:52,160 --> 00:03:53,680
Can you send me a bodyguard?

85
00:03:53,960 --> 00:03:54,320
Okay.

86
00:03:54,720 --> 00:03:55,480
