95
00:04:15,380 --> 00:04:16,960
Yunshu, I'll return to the police station

96
00:04:17,000 --> 00:04:18,710
and see if Mo Shenhai
has lodged a police report.

97
00:04:18,720 --> 00:04:19,610
I'll make a move first.

98
00:04:19,960 --> 00:04:20,600
Okay.

99
00:04:24,720 --> 00:04:26,000
