100
00:04:26,280 --> 00:04:27,400
I'll pack my belongings.

101
00:04:27,720 --> 00:04:28,000
Okay.

102
00:04:28,120 --> 00:04:28,920
Do you need my help?

103
00:04:29,040 --> 00:04:29,560
No.

104
00:04:30,840 --> 00:04:32,720
Please tell Chongming to help me.

105
00:04:34,640 --> 00:04:35,200
Chongming.

106
00:04:35,800 --> 00:04:37,680
Help my sister to her room.

107
00:04:56,000 --> 00:04:57,160
Thank you, Chongming.

108
00:05:12,680 --> 00:05:13,480
Long'er,

109
00:05:13,500 --> 00:05:14,960
I'm here to deliver dumplings to you.

110
00:05:15,080 --> 00:05:15,760
Open the door.

111
