117
00:05:29,800 --> 00:05:30,900
You should come out and eat.

118
00:05:31,040 --> 00:05:32,000
Now, you're a mortal.

119
00:05:32,010 --> 00:05:33,240
You'll starve if you don't eat.

120
00:05:34,160 --> 00:05:35,520
That's none of your business.

121
00:05:37,080 --> 00:05:37,640
Long'er,

122
00:05:38,320 --> 00:05:39,480
that's enough of you.

123
00:05:39,960 --> 00:05:41,000
You're a grown man.

124
00:05:41,160 --> 00:05:42,240
You're the dragon prince,

125
00:05:42,250 --> 00:05:43,870
yet you're holding a grudge
against a woman like me.

126
00:05:43,880 --> 00:05:46,190
If people hear about this,
they'll think that you're petty.

127
00:05:53,960 --> 00:05:55,200
Is he not inside?

128
00:05:58,680 --> 00:06:00,560
I'll leave the dumplings outside, then.

129
00:06:32,560 --> 00:06:33,320
Your Highness,

130
00:06:33,440 --> 00:06:34,990
you're finally willing to show yourself.

131
00:06:35,240 --> 00:06:36,960
