a petty woman, you know?

132
00:06:39,000 --> 00:06:40,990
Are you here to apologize
or make me angry again?

133
00:06:42,560 --> 00:06:43,080
Fine.

134
00:06:43,260 --> 00:06:43,960
I'll stop talking.

135
00:06:44,000 --> 00:06:45,200
You should hurry and eat up.

136
00:06:45,280 --> 00:06:45,880
