138
00:06:52,120 --> 00:06:53,000
Hurry and eat.

139
00:06:53,160 --> 00:06:54,040
Stop being stubborn.

140
00:06:54,660 --> 00:06:55,700
Do you know your fault now?

141
00:06:55,880 --> 00:06:56,560
I do.

142
00:06:57,000 --> 00:06:57,960
