144
00:06:59,560 --> 00:07:00,360
will be my fault.

145
00:07:00,680 --> 00:07:01,280
Look at you.

146
00:07:01,880 --> 00:07:03,040
You're doing this on purpose.

147
00:07:03,360 --> 00:07:04,720
You care about that man.

148
00:07:05,160 --> 00:07:06,640
You care about your sister.

149
00:07:07,220 --> 00:07:09,200
You care about
any random strangers on the road.

150
00:07:09,720 --> 00:07:11,140
But you don't care about me at all.

151
00:07:12,080 --> 00:07:12,960
Who said so?

152
00:07:13,240 --> 00:07:14,600
Of course I care about you.

153
00:07:14,680 --> 00:07:15,880
I knew that you were hungry.

154
00:07:16,000 --> 00:07:17,620
That's why I delivered dumplings to you.

155
00:07:18,810 --> 00:07:20,560
You vent your frustrations
on me every time.

156
00:07:20,760 --> 00:07:22,480
It's either you humiliate me
or punish me.

157
00:07:23,120 --> 00:07:24,160
I'm your bodyguard,

158
00:07:24,480 --> 00:07:25,480
not your fault.

159
00:07:26,510 --> 00:07:27,800
If you keep this up, I'll resign.

160
00:07:28,280 --> 00:07:29,120
Fine, fine.

161
00:07:29,560 --> 00:07:31,440
I'll care more about you in the future.

162
00:07:31,480 --> 00:07:32,640
I'll consider your feelings.

163
00:07:33,760 --> 00:07:34,560
Prove yourself.

164
00:07:35,080 --> 00:07:35,890
I'll do it next time.

165
00:07:39,200 --> 00:07:39,880
Shan Yunshu.

166
00:07:41,381 --> 00:07:42,080
What's the matter?

167
00:07:42,150 --> 00:07:44,110
Someone has reported you
for committing homicide.

168
00:07:44,120 --> 00:07:45,080
Come with us.

169
00:07:53,040 --> 00:07:53,600
It's fine.

170
00:07:54,080 --> 00:07:55,120
Finish the dumplings first.

171
00:08:04,120 --> 00:08:05,440
