172
00:08:07,480 --> 00:08:08,680
This beef jerky is excellent.

173
00:08:08,820 --> 00:08:09,440
Give it a try.

174
00:08:10,040 --> 00:08:11,280
Don't try to shift the topic.

175
00:08:11,880 --> 00:08:13,200
Where did you keep the record

176
00:08:13,380 --> 00:08:14,120
after stealing it?

177
00:08:15,220 --> 00:08:15,800
I destroyed it.

178
00:08:16,250 --> 00:08:17,990
What else did you think
I could do with it?

179
00:08:20,480 --> 00:08:22,480
This cotton candy is delicious too.

180
00:08:22,800 --> 00:08:24,190
I'm sure you never tried it before.

181
00:08:26,520 --> 00:08:27,680
You're so loyal

182
00:08:28,160 --> 00:08:29,720
to Mo Shenhai.

183
00:08:30,640 --> 00:08:32,880
You even resorted to
betraying your own sister.

184
00:08:33,960 --> 00:08:34,760
Chongming,

185
00:08:35,440 --> 00:08:37,200
Yuzi sent you here to look after me,

186
00:08:38,080 --> 00:08:39,560
not to interrogate me.

187
00:08:42,710 --> 00:08:43,380
Don't you agree?

188
00:08:46,280 --> 00:08:47,080
Are you trying

189
00:08:48,160 --> 00:08:50,280
to get me away from your sister

190
00:08:51,550 --> 00:08:53,480
so that you could launch
a sneak attack on her?

191
00:08:54,000 --> 00:08:54,990
Here's a piece of advice.

192
00:08:55,000 --> 00:08:55,930
Don't waste your effort.

193
00:08:58,120 --> 00:08:58,880
What are you doing?

194
00:08:59,280 --> 00:09:01,400
You may look like a silent person,

195
00:09:01,670 --> 00:09:03,500
but you're much more
talkative than I thought.

196
00:09:03,580 --> 00:09:04,240
Aren't you tired?

197
00:09:05,520 --> 00:09:06,880
Do you like Shan Yunshu?

198
00:09:10,880 --> 00:09:11,560
So what if I do?

199
00:09:12,480 --> 00:09:13,320
So what if I don't?

200
00:09:14,000 --> 00:09:15,180
That's none of your business.

201
00:09:15,760 --> 00:09:17,080
Everyone in Mo City likes her.

202
00:09:18,480 --> 00:09:19,680
Do you think we look alike?

203
00:09:24,120 --> 00:09:24,680
A little.

204
00:09:25,040 --> 00:09:25,890
Do you like me, then?

205
00:09:28,680 --> 00:09:29,480
I do.

206
00:09:31,320 --> 00:09:32,640
I like to roast you,

207
00:09:33,080 --> 00:09:33,960
dip you in sauces,

208
00:09:34,720 --> 00:09:36,960
