Let go of me.

218
00:09:51,880 --> 00:09:52,920
Why are you dragging me?

219
00:09:53,840 --> 00:09:55,680
Why are you shy with your food?

220
00:09:56,160 --> 00:09:57,520
What's with the outdated mindset?

221
00:09:57,960 --> 00:09:58,800
What exactly are you?

222
00:09:59,320 --> 00:10:00,200
How long can you live?

223
00:10:00,920 --> 00:10:02,400
Are you older than

224
00:10:02,480 --> 00:10:03,720
my grandfather's grandfather?

225
00:10:06,520 --> 00:10:07,320
Shan Yunshu,

226
00:10:08,240 --> 00:10:09,840
last night, someone reported

227
00:10:10,380 --> 00:10:12,280
that you had committed
a homicide at the pier.

228
00:10:12,800 --> 00:10:13,560
Do you confess?

229
00:10:14,640 --> 00:10:16,040
Mo Shenhai lodged the report, right?

230
00:10:17,000 --> 00:10:18,320
I did beat him up last night.

231
00:10:18,480 --> 00:10:20,040
I'm willing to bear the responsibility

232
00:10:20,280 --> 00:10:21,120
and compensation.

233
00:10:22,210 --> 00:10:23,990
It's good
that you're confessing your crime.

234
00:10:24,180 --> 00:10:26,920
I'm just afraid that you can't afford
to bear the responsibility.

235
00:10:33,000 --> 00:10:33,860
Who are these people?

236
00:10:34,300 --> 00:10:35,290
Don't you recognize them?

237
00:10:36,680 --> 00:10:39,480
