you allowed your bodyguard to take.

238
00:10:40,100 --> 00:10:41,440
There's a total of seven victims.

239
00:10:42,800 --> 00:10:43,480
Ms. Shan,

240
00:10:44,160 --> 00:10:45,640
don't you think you're too reckless?

241
00:10:46,560 --> 00:10:48,120
