just to locate you.

267
00:11:46,160 --> 00:11:47,480
You mustn't

268
00:11:49,160 --> 00:11:50,040
let her down.

269
00:11:50,800 --> 00:11:52,320
Do you care about her that much?

270
00:11:53,880 --> 00:11:55,520
Of course I do.

271
00:11:56,640 --> 00:11:57,760
We have

272
00:11:58,240 --> 00:12:00,280
the Dragon Pearl Pact.

273
00:12:02,560 --> 00:12:03,160
Dragon Pearl?

274
00:12:03,600 --> 00:12:04,320
That's right.

275
00:12:04,800 --> 00:12:05,520
The Dragon Pearl

276
00:12:05,690 --> 00:12:07,200
